---
import Image from "../common/Image.astro";

const heroDashboardImage = '~/assets/images/hero-dashboard.png';
---

<div
  class="flex w-full flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center py-20 sm:py-24 px-8"
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl w-full flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
    <!-- Teksto blokas -->
    <div class="flex-[1.4] text-center sm:text-left">
      <h1
        class="mx-auto relative max-w-4xl text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-normal text-white-300"
      >
        Automatizuota procesų
        <span class="relative whitespace-nowrap text-white-600">valdymo</span>
        <span class="relative whitespace-nowrap text-accent">
          <span class="">sistema</span>
          <svg
            aria-hidden="true"
            viewBox="0 0 418 42"
            class="h-[0.58em] w-80 fill-accent absolute sm:top-16 md:top-16"
            preserveAspectRatio="none"
          >
            <path
              d="M203.371.916c-26.013-2.078-76.686 1.963-124.73 9.946L67.3 12.749C35.421 18.062 18.2 21.766 6.004 25.934 1.244 27.561.828 27.778.874 28.61c.07 1.214.828 1.121 9.595-1.176 9.072-2.377 17.15-3.92 39.246-7.496C123.565 7.986 157.869 4.492 195.942 5.046c7.461.108 19.25 1.696 19.17 2.582-.107 1.183-7.874 4.31-25.75 10.366-21.992 7.45-35.43 12.534-36.701 13.884-2.173 2.308-.202 4.407 4.442 4.734 2.654.187 3.263.157 15.593-.78 35.401-2.686 57.944-3.488 88.365-3.143 46.327.526 75.721 2.23 130.788 7.584 19.787 1.924 20.814 1.98 24.557 1.332l.066-.011c1.201-.203 1.53-1.825.399-2.335-2.911-1.31-4.893-1.604-22.048-3.261-57.509-5.556-87.871-7.36-132.059-7.842-23.239-.254-33.617-.116-50.627.674-11.629.54-42.371 2.494-46.696 2.967-2.359.259 8.133-3.625 26.504-9.81 23.239-7.825 27.934-10.149 28.304-14.005 .417-4.348-3.529-6-16.878-7.066Z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </span>
      </h1>
      <p
        class="my-8 sm:my-16 text-center sm:text-left max-w-xl text-lg text-white-500 leading-7"
      >
        Vecticum – tai sprendimai verslui greičiau ir paprasčiau atlikti visus
        procesus nuo sąskaitų ir atostogų tvirtinimo iki specializuotų sprendimų
        individualiems poreikiams. Mes automatizuojame kasdieninius verslo
        procesus.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center sm:justify-start gap-4">
        <a
          class="rounded-full bg-accent px-5 sm:px-8 py-2.5 sm:py-3 text-base font-medium text-white shadow"
          href="https://app.vecticum.com/"
          target="_blank"
        >
          Išbandyti
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Vaizdo blokas -->
    <div class="flex-[1.1] flex flex-col justify-center sm:justify-end mt-12 sm:mt-0 space-y-4">
      <Image src={heroDashboardImage} alt="Verslo procesų valdymo sistema | VECTICUM" class="w-[80%] sm:w-full max-w-[500px] object-cover mx-auto" />
      <div class="flex flex-row justify-center gap-2 sm:gap-4">
        <img
          src="/media/services/ISO27001.jpg"
          alt="ISO Certification"
          class="w-32 sm:w-32 h-16 max-w-[100px] sm:max-w-[100px] object-contain grayscale"
        />
        <img
          src="/media/services/google-cloud-emblem.png"
          alt="Certification 2"
          class="w-32 sm:w-32 h-16 max-w-[100px] sm:max-w-[100px] object-contain grayscale"
        />
        <img
          src="/media/services/eidas-emblem.png"
          alt="Certification 3"
          class="w-32 sm:w-32 h-16 max-w-[100px] sm:max-w-[100px] object-contain grayscale"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>